 its a pain to med it up.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Jul 31 10:42:55 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Venerable Karanthal Everglade<br>Storm Warden.</td></tr>
